parts:
{
  "prompt": "Design a traditional letterhead for Lumina Solar Commercial, incorporating elements that reflect the solar energy industry. The letterhead should feature a clean, professional layout with a solar panel motif subtly integrated into the background or header. Include a top section with the company name, 'Lumina Solar Commercial,' in elegant, modern typography. Below the company name, provide space for the address, phone number, and email address, represented as placeholders: 'Address Line 1, City, State, ZIP', 'Phone: (000) 000-0000', 'Email: info@luminasolar.com'. The overall design should convey sustainability, innovation, and professionalism, with a color scheme that includes shades of blue, green, and yellow to represent the sun, technology, and the environment.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "Create a professional letterhead for Lumina Solar Commercial using the provided format and logo. The letterhead should be clean and modern, with IBM Blue as the primary color. Subtly incorporate an image of solar panels in Washington DC into the background or header, ensuring the solar panel image is very subtle and does not overpower the layout. The company logo should be prominently placed, and the design should include placeholders for the company’s address, phone number, and email in a manner that matches the elegance and sophistication of the provided format. The layout should be suitable for a business letter, with space at the top for the company's contact information and a footer section for additional details.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "Design a simple and elegant letterhead for Lumina Solar Commercial with a white background. Use the IBM Blue color for the text and design elements. The letterhead should feature the company's logo at the top, followed by placeholders for the company’s contact information like address, phone number, and email, which should be in a clean and modern font. Incorporate a very faint watermark of solar panels in the background, ensuring it's barely noticeable to maintain the simplicity of the design. The footer should have a subtle line in IBM Blue with the company's web address in small, discreet text. The overall design should be minimalistic, with lots of white space and no other colors or images to keep the focus on the content of the letter.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "Design a simple and refined letterhead for Lumina Solar Commercial with a white background, making the heading smaller than the previous version. Utilize IBM Blue for the text and design elements. Position the company's logo at the top center, but ensure it's less prominent, followed by placeholders for the company’s contact information such as address, phone number, and email in a clean, modern, smaller font. Include a very subtle watermark of solar panels in the background, but make it almost imperceptible to keep the design clean. The footer should have a discreet line in IBM Blue with the company's web address in small text. The design should be minimalistic, with ample white space to emphasize the content of the letter.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "Design a simple and sophisticated letterhead for Lumina Solar Commercial with a white background. Use IBM Blue for the text and subtle design accents. Place the company's logo at the top center, but make it smaller and less prominent than before. Add placeholders for the company’s contact information in a clean, modern, and smaller font. Incorporate an extremely faint watermark of the Capitol Building in Washington DC, behind the text area to add a local touch without distracting from the overall simplicity of the design. Ensure the watermark is almost imperceptible. The footer should feature a fine line in IBM Blue with the company's web address in tiny text. Maintain a minimalistic design with plenty of white space.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "Design a minimalistic and professional letterhead for Lumina Solar Commercial with a white background. Incorporate a subtle image of the Capitol Building in Washington DC, faintly visible in the background to not distract from the content. The heading, featuring the company's logo, should be smaller and placed at the top center using IBM Blue for the company name. Place placeholders for the company's contact information in a smaller, modern font below the logo. Maintain a clean and uncluttered design with a footer that includes a discreet IBM Blue line and the company's web address in small text. The overall look should be elegant, with the Capitol Building image adding a touch of locality without overwhelming the design.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "Design an ultra-minimalistic letterhead for Lumina Solar Commercial with a white background. The design should feature a very faint silhouette of the Capitol Building in Washington DC as a watermark in the background. Use IBM Blue for the text, with the company's logo at the top center, but make it very small and unobtrusive. Below the logo, include placeholders for the company's contact information in a simple, small, and modern font. The footer should be almost plain, with only a thin line in IBM Blue and the company's web address in very small text. There should be a vast amount of white space to keep the focus on the letter's content, with every design element being as subtle as possible.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "Design an extremely minimalistic letterhead for Lumina Solar Commercial, maintaining a white background and subtle design elements. The top should feature the company's logo in IBM Blue, but scaled down significantly to keep the focus on simplicity. Beneath the logo, include the bare minimum contact information using a very small, modern font. Integrate an almost imperceptible watermark of the Capitol Building in Washington DC in the background. The footer should have just a single, fine line in IBM Blue with the company's web address in tiny font. The overall design should prioritize a clean and spacious layout with minimal distractions.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
